data.description: Meticulously kept 2 bed 2 bath second story condo in desirable River Terrace East. This building is secure and requires keyed access to internal units. Step inside and enjoy the vaulted great room with bedrooms on opposite sides of this floorplan, with the Main having a generous walk in closet. As a bonus, the gym and pool are located just downstairs. Excellent location!
